    <mxCell id="6" value="&lt;b&gt;③ Multer — File Upload Handler&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Lưu file vào /public/uploads/&lt;br/&gt;Validate: mimetype trong [image/jpeg, image/png, image/webp]&lt;br/&gt;maxFileSize = 10 MB"
      style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#16A34A;strokeColor=#15803D;fontColor=#FFFFFF;fontSize=11;"
